[{"id":"1127fb633a60fe602b7b0811995783a5","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Stotter, Manuela","to_list":[{"name":"Stotter, Manuela","email":"MStotter@Related.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: catch up","date":"2008-01-14T17:02:49.000Z","formatted_date":"Jan 14, 2008","formatted_time":"5:02 PM","body":"I won'tbe back intil friday\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: \"Stotter, Manuela\" <MStotter@Related.com>\nTo: jeeproject@yahoo.com\nSent: Monday, January 14, 2008 11:03:09 AM\nSubject: catch up\n\n\nHallo Jeffrey,\n \nI\u2019m sorry I missed you last week. I really hoped to see you and catch up a bit. I know you are quite busy and my schedule is not as flexible any more.\nI may just stop by at your office to say HI to everybody, but I really wanted to see you. I always feel that at the end you were the only person who believed in me and gave me the opportunity to come to NYC.\nMy life changed very much and now I\u2019m very stable and happy. I would not be where I\u2019m without your initial support.\nWell, that\u2019s all. THANKS was the only thing I came to say to you.\n \nLet me know if you ever want to see me and I can stop at 9th 71st street .\n \nHave a good day, wherever you are today,\n \nM\n \nManuela E. St\u00f6tter\nRELATED\n60 Columbus Circle\nNew York, NY 10023\nTel: 212.801.3796\nCell: 917.498.5285\nFax: 212.801.3727\nwww.related.com","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">I won'tbe back intil friday<BR><BR>\n<DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">----- Original Message ----<BR>From: \"Stotter, Manuela\" &lt;MStotter@Related.com&gt;<BR>To: jeeproject@yahoo.com<BR>Sent: Monday, January 14, 2008 11:03:09 AM<BR>Subject: catch up<BR><BR>\n<STYLE>\n<!--\n _fi