 would not be where I\u2019m without your initial support.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">Well, that\u2019s all. THANKS was the only thing I came to say to you.</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">Let me know if you ever want to see me and I can stop at 9<SUP>th</SUP> 71<SUP>st</SUP> street .</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">Have a good day, wherever you are today,</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">M</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Comic Sans MS\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Comic Sans MS'\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><EM><I><FONT face=Papyrus color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Papyrus\">Manuela E. St\u00f6tter</SPAN></FONT></I></EM><FONT color=navy><SPAN style=\"COLOR: navy\"></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=\"Copperplate Gothic Light\" color=navy size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: 'Copperplate Goth